<div class="modal-content">
    <header class="modal-header">
        <h1>优惠链接</h1>
    </header>
    <button type="button" class="close" title="Close" {{on "click" @close}}>{{svg-jar "close"}}<span class="hidden">关闭</span></button>

    <div class="modal-body">
        <p>
        您可以在任何地方共享此链接。在您的推送、社交媒体、播客或面对面。这一切都很管用。        </p>
        <div class="gh-input-group">
            <GhTextInput
                @name="url"
                @value={{this.offerUrl}}
                @id="url"
                @disabled="disabled"
                @class="gh-input" />

            <GhTaskButton
                @buttonText="Copy link"
                @task={{this.copyOfferUrl}}
                @successText="Link copied"
                @class="gh-btn gh-btn-black gh-btn-icon" />
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
